dct_title_s: Chart of the Delaware River Along the Camden Waterfront from Newton Creek to Cooper Point II
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Newton Creek to Cooper Point in Camden along the Delaware River. Map shows water depths of the Delaware River and includes properties and businesses along the river, as well as road names and pierhead/bulkhead lines.
